    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Doorway Effect</strong> is a 1-4 player co-op survival horror roguelike. Venture into the subconscious minds of test subjects, investigating the recesses of  their psyche to dissect a lifetime of fears and traumas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/1fed1f3e5e0174c06fc93bab2b2500c6.poster.avif?t=1757698026\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/1fed1f3e5e0174c06fc93bab2b2500c6.webm?t=1757698026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/1fed1f3e5e0174c06fc93bab2b2500c6.mp4?t=1757698026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/8443265b62be7acd89856d705f3d6529.webp?t=1757698026\" width=616 height=35 /></span>While you can still play and enjoy the game solo, we know there's no better feeling than getting scared half to death alongside other people. <strong>The Doorway Effect</strong> will primarily be a multiplayer experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/8ae3385d8953d2d8808dc3cff62b3e26.poster.avif?t=1757698026\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/8ae3385d8953d2d8808dc3cff62b3e26.webm?t=1757698026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/8ae3385d8953d2d8808dc3cff62b3e26.mp4?t=1757698026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/1708f97ec79c98b6eea6b1c3e9cb4e6d.webp?t=1757698026\" width=616 height=35 /></span>This game is atmospheric, frightening, and filled with secrets. There's no telling what may be waiting beyond each door. Collect keys, solve puzzles, outsmart the entities, and brace yourself for the worst... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/e53bb5d49c745bf9206adf184f44c477.poster.avif?t=1757698026\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/e53bb5d49c745bf9206adf184f44c477.webm?t=1757698026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/e53bb5d49c745bf9206adf184f44c477.mp4?t=1757698026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326550/extras/2e3a22ad72942ae361ad31ba88196636.webp?t=1757698026\" width=616 height=35 /></span>Push forward through 100s of doors in a shapeshifting environment, scrambling to escape the horrors within, and to reach the final Doorway. Run after run, make it a little further each time, and attempt to unravel the larger mysteries at hand as you do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the cooperative horror of <i>Phasmophobia</i> and <i>Lethal Company</i>, the randomized gameplay of <i>Doors</i>, and the existentialism of <i>The Stanley Parable</i>.</p>",
